Firepile 0.1 -- OpenCL GPU Programming with Scala
----------------------------------------------------

To compile Firepile:

$ sbt compile

To compile test cases:

$ sbt test-compile

To run:

$ bin/firepile firepile.tests.Foo

NOTE: You will need to modify $SCALA_LIB_JAR in bin/firepile to point to your
Scala installation's scala-library.jar

---------------------------------------------------
Examples to try:

firepile.tests.ReduceModifiedPlusBB <n>

<n> - 2 ^ n randomly generated elements to reduce (default 20)

 
firepile.tests.TestBlackScholesModified <n>

<n> - n * 1000000 options (default 4)




